---

End-of-life home: patient-centered + goals. Multidisciplinary including hospice. Functional optimization w/in prognosis. Symptom mgmt. Caregiver. Advance planning. Spiritual. Hospice eligibility. Bereavement. Cultural. Modern integrated.'
