---

ALS multidisciplinary clinic (improves survival). Symptom-targeted: dysphagia/PEG + AAC + NIV + cough assist + mobility (no overuse) + spasticity + sialorrhea + PBA + mood. DMT (riluzole etc). Advance planning early. Caregiver.'
