GBS rehab: phased multidisciplinary. AVOID overuse weakness (submaximal). Pulm (cough assist, IMT, VC). Dysautonomia (ortho). Pain + fatigue + mood + sensory + dysphagia. DVT. Family. Long-term residual. Modern structured.'
